  "ice-lord": "An ice lord is the elemental lord of cold, one of the very powerful elemental beings that come and go between the planes and the human world as they please,…",
  "magmani": "The magmani is the elemental lord of fire, one of the very powerful elemental beings that come and go between the planes and the human world as they please,…",
