  "sea-king": "A sea-king is the elemental lord of water, one of the very powerful elemental beings that come and go between the planes and the human world as they please,…",
  "white-pasha": "A white pasha is the elemental lord of light, one of the very powerful elemental beings that come and go between the planes and the human world as they…",
