  "gnom": "Elementals are incarnations of the elements, summoned from the elemental planes into our world by a magician's elemental magic.",
  "luminal": "Luminals are the elementals of light, incarnations of that element summoned from its plane into our world by elemental magic and bound to the will of the…",
